The global fibrate drugs market is witnessing growth due to the increasing prevalence of cardiovascular diseases and hyperlipidemia, which has led to a rise in the demand for cholesterol-lowering medications. The market is also being driven by the growing awareness about the importance of maintaining healthy cholesterol levels and the effectiveness of fibrate drugs in managing lipid profiles. Moreover, advancements in drug delivery systems and formulations are expected to further boost market growth.

